1. add a httpclient, which is used for communication between java plugin and py server. 2. complete updateData() func in MainToolWindow, now the data in plugin can update real time.
1. InvokeAction now can communicate with remote server and update retrieved code snippets.

1. combine config (e.g. useBert ) with remote search.
1. add "tokenSequence" filed in Indexer 2. add MultiFieldsQueryBuilder
1. update SLP-Core.jar (for "lineCodes" in the extracted current method)
1. fix bug that local mode cannot be retrieved immediately.
1. update SLPCore, update "extractCurrentMethod" 2. send contextCode -> send contextCodeTokens
1. update GUI (remove "score"&"title board", remove useless buttons in main panel)
